{"tid":1668143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講晒，支唔支持加泰係我地每個人既自由","createTime":"2019-10-21T23:59:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T08:56:31.000Z","uid":34816,"like":74,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e5d46bbaff49384dd4335831dd4f0ff2e53cd05e","tid":1668143,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T23:59:20.000Z","msg":"當自己有事就想全世界都幫手，但人地地方有同樣問題就連發聲都話驚得罪人？<br />\n<br />\n咁不如番去奶共算啦，講咩野fight for freedom？講咩野民主自由人權？講咩野黑白良知？<br />\n<br />\n加泰集會，想去就去，想支持就支持，呢個係我地每個人都有既權利同自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4573c2e4bcc7130e30c1e3d362c399b2a07203c5","tid":1668143,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T00:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b18115426af33876eeafd1a48a05924b97df183","tid":1668143,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T00:00:41.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"4bb41111398ef7610998b26c2fd6951129aefe85","tid":1668143,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T00:02:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加泰爭議既解決方案</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668004</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c5f9ad388ad8a2301a1b7383d171e2d0290734a1","tid":1668143,"uid":99124,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T00:04:17.000Z","msg":"無錯，我地無大台，無統一意見，大家覺得岩就去支持加泰人民。每個人都享有自由意志。"},{"pid":"e22af93ee1713451cb82199ff85b7a6befc87cdb","tid":1668143,"uid":98993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T00:06:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a525f3752f5351e2bbe731fbd7ade56f60d880c","tid":1668143,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c5f9ad388ad8a2301a1b7383d171e2d0290734a1","tid":1668143,"uid":99124,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"